def tables_tables_openofficexml_put_id(self, id, **kwargs)

Tables: Modify Underlying Xml # noqa: E501

Directly eidt the underlying xml of a Table object within an OpenOpenXml (e.g. Excel, Powerpoint) document. This endpoint will validatate the submitted xml against the Ecma-376 standard prior to saving modification. Invalid xml will rejected by this endpoint and a (hopefully) helpful error message will be returned. Use this endpoint for client-side automation of modifications ot Table objects. # noqa: E501 This method makes a synchronous HTTP request by default. To make an asynchronous HTTP request, please pass async_req=True

>>> thread = api.tables_tables_openofficexml_put_id(id, async_req=True)
>>> result = thread.get()
